text: Medeli also known as Henchir-Mencoub is a location and archaeology site in Tunisia , North Africa. Medeli was a Roman era town of the Roman Province of Africa Proconsularis, and lasted through the Roman, Vandal and Byzantine empires. ==References== Category:Roman towns and cities in Africa (Roman province) Category:Catholic titular sees in Africa Category:Former Roman Catholic dioceses in Africa
title: Medeli
